Their First Mistake [1932] short 21 min B/W & Colour version

Mrs. Hardy is irate that her husband Oliver spends more time with his friend
Stanley than with her. Oliver decides to adopt a baby, hoping that it will keep
his wife occupied so that he and Stanley can continue to carouse. But upon
returning home with the infant, they find a process server with a divorce
summons, and spend a sleepless night caring for the squalling baby.

Starring: Stan Laurel, Oliver Hardy, Mae Busch, Billy Gilbert,
          Marjorie Campbell, George Marshall
Director: George Marshall
